[quest]Industrial Magic Matrix[/quest]

Twist's version of the Infusion Matrix from Thaumcraft. 

[warn]Use the Infusion Supplier to supply Essence[/warn]

[note]The Industrial Magic Matrix is unable to perform active infusions[/note]

Parallelism depends on the level of the structure block.

Has a 4/2 OC. You can turn on lossless overclocking after reaching the maximum acceeration rate. 

[note]Use Charged Nodes to get acceleration rewards[/note]

If the number of nodes is < 6, processing time will be §4recipe time * number of missing nodes * 1.75

§9There is more information on the ToolTip. Please refer to that for more information. 

§4[warn]This multi requires a lot of materials. Be sure to keep track of everything you need.[/warn]
